      About this item

      • Flexible Connectivity: These smart recessed downlights support Wi-Fi and Bluetooth direct control for more convenience. The connectivity options allow a more stable connection, unlike lights that only support Wi-Fi or Bluetooth.
      • Multiple Lighting Options: Select from 16 million colors and 1-100% dimmable brightness to make your space feel more vibrant. For more natural lighting, there are tunable 2700k-6500k warm white to cool daylight options for reading or relaxing.
      • Multi Scene Modes: Access an exciting variety of 65 preset scene modes inspired by nature, holidays, and more, with a simple tap on the Govee Home App. There is also a selection of fun music modes that match up with your favorite music(Govee Music Sync Box Required).
      • All-In-One Group Control: There is no need to change the colors or brightness manually. Use the Group Control feature to control all of your lights using the app. You can also adjust the lights in separate rooms by making them their own groups.
      • Two-Way Control: You can control your smart ceilingt lights on Govee Home App with a simple tap. These lights also support Alexa/Google Home to access Voice Control. *2.4GHz Wi-Fi only.
      • *Installation Tip: Press the spring clips into the holes to get it affixed to the light.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

          The products are as advertised and easy to install. I have included a picture of what comes with each light as I found that information lacking when I went through the product descriptions. Regardless on how many lights you buy in the package, each comes with the light, driver box, and connectors for wiring.
          Setup through the Govee app was simple and took less than 10 minutes to get all 8 lights I installed up and running.
          Overall, after a few days, I am happy with the product and would recommend if you are looking to add some additional lights to an area.

          Electrically, easy to install if you know what you are doing. Bigger challenge for me was to fish wires through a cramped attic space, but with the right tools and an extra set of hands, it worked out fairly well.
